  <Date>2026-01-29</Date>
  <Function>inja is a C++ templating engine. it generates strings based on a template and a data map as json. it can be used to generate source code based on structured data.</Function>
  <Justification>This will be a useful library for C++ and Verse code generation.</Justification>
